 2023 年 9 月 20 日起将猴痘纳入乙类传染病进行管理。中疾控 9 月 8 日发布的检测情况显示，中国内地（不含港澳台）8 月新增报告 501 例猴痘确诊病例，其中，首次报告 5 例女性病例。 「出现女性感染者，意味着我国猴痘感染人群进一步扩大。」南方医科大学公共卫生学院生物安全研究中心主任赵卫告诉人民日报健康客户端记者，从此次报告看，病例中的女性感染者发病前 21 天内均有异性性接触史，因此通过异性性接触感染可能性大。总体上来说，猴痘通过性接触以外的其他接触方式传播风险低，因此对普通人来说，只要性伴侣双方没有不洁性行为，感染的风险极低，在女性群体中出现大范围传播的可能性也极低。中国首次报告 5 例女性猴痘病例，「未来甚至可能出现家庭内传播」_ 生命科学 _ 澎湃新闻 -The Paper"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-1898c0cad287bc92590237ad61fdf93e_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "44 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/622561452"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIucWuhJGfg6ojEAMaCTEwMDYyNjQzMiDFh5+oBjAAOKABQBdyCTYyMjU2MTQ1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1695034939.580966", "card_id": "Q_21715274", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 69}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "四十岁以后你才明白的道理有哪些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-1f148feddd87e31793a92e8538a179d0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "40 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/21715274"}}, "attached_info": "CjwIucWuhJGfg6ojEAMaBjg2NzAzNSCV5JSSBTAAOPgCQBhyCDIxNzE1Mjc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1695034939.581975", "card_id": "Q_614984493", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 462}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子补习班都换了 5 个了，成绩却依然在原地踏步，怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-69f43fa7b94cf89097e3ecfee4029da0_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "li